OL,7,FDashcam footage of dangerous drivers
OL,8,Fcan be uploaded to police, changing
OL,9,Fthe way our roads are enforced, as ITV
OL,10,FNews' Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,11,Freports.
OL,13,FNew dashcam data obtained by ITV News
OL,14,Freveals the sheer scale of dangerous
OL,15,Fdriving.
OL,17,FThousands of road users have uploaded
OL,18,Ffootage to a portal which allows
OL,19,Fpolice to use the images as evidence -
OL,20,Fbut it's brought concern about what
OL,21,Fhas been called "DIY road cops".
