OL,7,FAround seven million vehicles now have
OL,8,Fdashcams, and our new data shows it's
OL,9,Fchanging how our roads are policed.
OL,11,FNew figures given to ITV News show
OL,12,F146,560 uploads to the National
OL,13,FDashcam Safety Portal, which allows
OL,14,Fpolice to use footage as evidence. So
OL,15,Ffar this year there have been 43,450
OL,16,Fclips sent to the system.
