OL,7,FThe dashcam portal also accepts mobile
OL,8,Fphone footage or clips from any
OL,9,Frecording device, but some people have
OL,10,Fquestioned whether this should all be
OL,11,Fleft to the professionals.
OL,13,FWe spoke to PC Darren Ferneyhough of
OL,14,Fthe West Midlands Police, he said: "We
OL,15,Faren't asking people to go out there
OL,16,Fand film on purpose, it is more ad-hoc
OL,17,Fand if they catch an offence on a
OL,18,Fdashcam and it is serious enough, we
OL,19,Fwill prosecute and take positive
OL,20,Faction."
