OL,7,FBy uploading video clips of dangerous
OL,8,Fdrivers, organisers of the dashcam
OL,9,Fportal estimate that the equivalent of
OL,10,Fmore than a century of police time has
OL,11,Fbeen saved.
OL,13,FBut with so much footage now being
OL,14,Fuploaded, is there a risk of swamping
OL,15,Fpolice? Bryn Brooker is a dashcam
OL,16,Fexpert from the Nextbase tech company.
