OL,3,CPortal for uploading dashcam footage
OL,4,Csaves 'more than a century of police
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FHe said: "The great thing about the
OL,8,FNational Dashcam Safety Portal is it
OL,9,Fis helping police process evidence
OL,10,Ffaster. They can process ten pieces of
OL,11,Fevidence in less than 30 minutes.
OL,13,F"At the moment, around 70% of all
OL,14,Fuploads are actioned. So that action
OL,15,Fcan range from anywhere up to a
OL,16,Fwarning letter, right the way through
OL,17,Fto prosecution in court."
