OL,7,FTo upload video, road users can search
OL,8,Fonline for the National Dashcam Safety
OL,9,FPortal. Scotland isn't yet part of the
OL,10,Fsystem but there are plans to change
OL,11,Fthat, as millions of dashcams give
OL,12,Fpolice an unprecedented view of what's
OL,13,Fgoing wrong on our roads.
OL,15,FTo upload dashcam or other footage of
OL,16,Froad incidents, visit the portal here.
